743
01:43:25,950 --> 01:43:28,451
Even when God seemed to have abandoned me...

744
01:43:28,619 --> 01:43:30,120
He was watching.

745
01:43:30,288 --> 01:43:33,081
Even when He seemed indifferent to my suffering...

746
01:43:33,249 --> 01:43:34,708
He was watching.

747
01:43:34,876 --> 01:43:38,712
And when I was beyond all hope 
of saving, He gave me rest...

748
01:43:38,880 --> 01:43:41,965
